{"tid":1245549,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"101拘捕令 - 香港警察因濫暴襲擊示威者而被群眾拘捕","createTime":"2019-06-20T10:52:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-20T12:02:28.000Z","uid":259055,"like":38,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"368f3e73517ac2837cc5ceb9b301dafacd698f12","tid":1245549,"uid":259055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T10:52:48.000Z","msg":"近日，警員濫權濫打濫捕示威者嘅新聞不絕於耳，(例子唔多講<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />) 呢啲行為實屬違法，作為良好市民又豈可視而不見？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n小弟雨革嗰陣學識咗個term叫 &quot;公民拘捕&quot;，又名「101 拘捕令」，係香港刑事訴訟程序條例第 221 章 101 條賦予任何人（即係普通市民都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）喺無需手令嘅情況下逮捕疑犯嘅權力。<br />\n<br />\n而且為達逮捕目的，行使此權力的人士可使用<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>合理的武力制服疑犯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span>，在面對可判處超過12個月監禁的罪時近日，(包括普通襲擊、 襲擊致造成身體傷害、傷人19、傷人17<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)，等警察到場或將疑犯押到警署。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當然成個拘捕過程要拍晒片，就算自己友嚟到救走佢，我地都可以將呢啲片推到上國際層面，等國際傳媒笑鳩到香港警察面黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇得諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6adab19baa9304461902944a417d11287471ff0","tid":1245549,"uid":259055,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T10:53:46.000Z","msg":"只要人夠多<br />\n事就變得好辦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3525f91fb0dd67194d9a39a1e51d60638c2a78d1","tid":1245549,"uid":259055,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T10:55:18.000Z","msg":"傳媒影住熱心市民將濫暴警員押送番去警署<br />\n咪話唔爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c17df025e8d2d925ff41e068b37f21b39771cac1","tid":1245549,"uid":259055,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T10:57:35.000Z","msg":"支唔支持都留個言比下意見啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5816d3b59054820eab883d469c7cdf768918d98","tid":1245549,"uid":260653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T10:59:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df6e6bda1fcb35f9aab824f8e4d6dfab8416fffc","tid":1245549,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T10:59:50.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"9bafa31321e921f7f42a851893158e9eed9ba776","tid":1245549,"uid":259055,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T11:02:05.000Z","msg":"如果疑犯爭扎<br />\n我地可以用索帶捆綁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f258770c4a91e0d8d7ee06adaff4c888d10bcd1d","tid":1245549,"uid":259055,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T11:06:25.000Z","msg":"設計對白: <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n呢位警員，剛才我見到你使用不要必武力蓄意襲擊呢位市民，我地有理由相信你已觸犯普通襲擊罪/傷人17, 19，而家我地行使101拘捕令將你拘捕，請你合作，如果唔係我地會用適當武力將你制服</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"22a290a0e5e678bd3a3f42fb78caf9fb7813173b","tid":1245549,"uid":59633,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T11:09:12.000Z","msg":"同狗講101拘捕令<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48e04693ec128e9ab5856d22463212c0bb666662","tid":1245549,"uid":259055,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"22a290a0e5e678bd3a3f42fb78caf9fb7813173b","tid":1245549,"uid":59633,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T11:09:12.000Z","msg":"同狗講101拘捕令<i